author: stsp
msg: Enable TCP keep-alives in the svnserve server.
ra_svn clients have been using TCP keep-alives since r37890.
This shouldn't hurt, and may even fix hanging svnserve processes
reported by user KotH in #svn.
* subversion/svnserve/main.c
(main): Try to enable keep-alives after accepting a client connection.
